==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One word has the weight of nine bronze [[鼎|Ding]] vessels.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī yán jĭu dĭng

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[言]][[九]][[鼎]]'''

# A solemn promise or pledge.

